{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","data":{"alias":"cindery-thickset-flyingfox","description":"## Summary\ntests/external/test_link_sync_roundtrip_live.py::test_link_sync_differ_apply_roundtrip_live fails on main with:\n  AttributeError: 'StubBindingStore' object has no attribute 'get_baseline'\nThe reconciler per-binding-baseline path was finalized (baseline rollout flags retired, e.g. c4d58a306), so outbound_fields.py:418 now ALWAYS calls binding_store.get_baseline(local_id) (comment at :410). The integration-tier stubs were updated with get_baseline, but the external-tier StubBindingStore (tests/external/test_link_sync_roundtrip_live.py:126) was missed — the one sibling not updated.\n\n## Reproduction Steps\n1. Run the external-integration workflow on main (workflow_dispatch). Observed run 29303295904 (2026-07-14): '1 failed, 24 passed' — only test_link_sync_differ_apply_roundtrip_live fails on the missing-attribute AttributeError.\nExpected: the external stub implements the BindingStore.get_baseline(local_id)->dict|None contract; absent baseline returns None (local-wins, ADR 0026 §2), matching the stub's pre-flag behavior.\nActual: the stub lacks the method; the outbound arbitration path AttributeErrors.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] StubBindingStore in tests/external/test_link_sync_roundtrip_live.py implements get_baseline(local_id)->dict|None matching binding_store.BindingStore.get_baseline (return None = no last-synced baseline).\n- [ ] [operator-attested] external-integration workflow re-run on main is green (test_link_sync_differ_apply_roundtrip_live passes) — live-Jira tier, verified by a workflow re-run.\n- [ ] No other external/integration BindingStore stub is left missing get_baseline where the outbound arbitration path exercises it (sibling sweep: integration stubs already updated; only this external one was missed).","id":"5e55-9bfa-ac57-4a6a","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"external-tier StubBindingStore missing get_baseline after reconciler baseline rollout finalized — test_link_sync_differ_apply_roundtrip_live fails"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1784000033112439001,"uuid":"98969ccf-0c8b-4f20-bc21-918e60106f97"}